name: Www-scraper-digitalarkivet
tagline: Project for harvesting metadata from DigitalArkivet
body:
### Welcome to the project.
This Project is slowly developing. Main objective is to harvest metadata and build database for members of DIS-Norge, The Genealogy Society of Norway-DIS. 

### Authors and Contributors
Rolf B. Holte (@rholte)
Please drop me an email if you use this in any project. It would be nice to know if it's usable for others in any capacity. Any suggestions for improvement are also appreciated.

### Support or Contact
Having trouble? I'm not able to support this project on daily basis. Reach out and I'll get back to you as soon as I can
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
